OL,3,CPeople seeking help for chronic pain
OL,4,Cquadruples in four years in Jersey
OL,6,FThe number of people in Jersey seeking
OL,7,Fhelp for chronic pain has quadrupled
OL,8,Fover the past four years.
OL,10,FThe charity, Pain Support Jersey, has
OL,11,Fseen its membership increase from 64
OL,12,Fin 2020, to 260 today.
OL,14,FDoctors estimate that 25 percent of
OL,15,Fislanders will be suffering with some
OL,16,Fform of chronic pain condition, with
OL,17,F10 percent of Jersey's working age
OL,18,Fpopulation struggling to maintain a
OL,19,Fjob because of it.
