OL,3,CPeople seeking help for chronic pain
OL,4,Cquadruples in four years in Jersey
OL,6,FHealth services in both Bailiwicks are
OL,7,Freporting a steady increase in demand,
OL,8,Fpartly due to an ageing population and
OL,9,Fpartly due to more sedentary and high
OL,10,Fstress lifestyles.
OL,12,FMovement and exercise are vital for
OL,13,Frecovery - Pain Support Jersey puts on
OL,14,Ffree classes twice a week aimed at
OL,15,Frelieving chronic pain.
