OL,3,CPeople seeking help for chronic pain
OL,4,Cquadruples in four years in Jersey
OL,6,FPhysiotherapist Mike Du Feu told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "With people with pain we tend
OL,8,Fto see a lot of bracing and muscular
OL,9,Ftension so part of the work that we do
OL,10,Fis try to help them reduce that
OL,11,Ftension and improve their movement and
OL,12,Fultimately their quality of life."
OL,14,FKerry Torpy, who suffers from hip pain
OL,15,Fafter she shattered her pelvis in a
OL,16,Fcar accident, says the classes have
OL,17,Fgiven her a new support network.
