OL,3,CPeople seeking help for chronic pain
OL,4,Cquadruples in four years in Jersey
OL,6,FShe said: "I feel more hopeful and
OL,7,Fsupported because being around people
OL,8,Fthat understand pain with you makes a
OL,9,Fbig difference. "
OL,11,FKate Kelly, from Pain Support Jersey,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We're a friendly group, we're
OL,13,Flike a big family and we come
OL,14,Ftogether, we lift each other up, we
OL,15,Fshare stories and there is lots and
OL,16,Flots of laughter along the way too."
